title: Man Ho
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A vegetarian and vegan friendly Chinese restaurant in the Bury Park area of Luton. Menu includes a large selection of vegetable-based dishes such a pak choi in a garlic sauce and stir fried vegetables. You can also order a mock chicken dish in any of the flavors available on the menu. For example black bean vegetarian chicken. The lunch, takeaway, and evening menus differ; however you can ask for anything you like from any menu. There is also live entertainment on the weekends.
